OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA wet
OL,6,Fevening and night to come with the
OL,7,Frain heavy and persistent at times,
OL,8,Fespecially over the hills. Windy
OL,9,Finitially, although easing later in
OL,10,Fthe night.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA wet start to the day,
OL,13,Fespecially in the south. Rain will
OL,14,Fclear to the east by the afternoon
OL,15,Fwith a mix of sunny spells and a few
OL,16,Fshowers following.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
